Package es.optocom.jovp.engine

Class Monitor

java.lang.Object
es.optocom.jovp.engine.Monitor
public class Monitor extends Object
Retrieves and stores the monitor capabilities including size in mm, pixel size for the calculation of the observer's field of view.
